09:51 <vmassol> mflorea: good morning

09:52 <vmassol> would you know why translations are missing from http://design.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/AppWithinMinutes/ ?  
09:52 <vmassol> I saw that there's a Translation page for AWM but it has no xobject for transaltion  
09:52 <vmassol> could that be the problem?  
09:52 <mflorea> probably the translation page was saved by someone with not enough rights for the level  
09:53 <gdelhumeau> has joined #xwiki  
09:53 <vmassol> ah yes just checked the sources in github  
09:53 <vmassol> and indeed there's an xobject there  
09:54 <vmassol> so maybe the AWM extension has not been updated, checking  
09:54 <mflorea> yes, https://github.com/xwiki/xwiki-platform/blob/xwiki-platform-8.2.1/xwiki-platform-core/xwiki-platform-appwithinminutes/xwiki-platform-appwithinminutes-ui/src/main/resources/AppWithinMinutes/Translations.xml#L213  
09:54 <vmassol> yep 6.4.1  
09:54 <mflorea> the object is there  
09:54 <mflorea> or maybe a bad merge  
09:54 <vmassol> however the extension doesn't appeazr in the EM updater  
09:54 <vmassol> I'll do it manually  
09:55 <mflorea> see what version is installed  
09:56 <mflorea> version 8.2.1 appears installed  
09:56 <vmassol> works now  
09:56 <vmassol> mflorea: I've upgraed it now :)  
09:57 <mflorea> ah, ok  
09:57 <vmassol> however I don't understand why EM updater was not proposing it  
09:57 <mflorea> did you upgrade or install?  
09:58 <mflorea> I see it was upgrade  
09:58 <mflorea> from 6.4.1
